    "attributes": {
        "action": "Establish discount scheme for cheaper books for schools, students and NHS staff",
        "additional_details": "So that students and NHS staff who don\u2019t have a lot of money can afford new books and then so that schools can get books for cheaper like new ones.",
        "background": "We want  the Government to set up a discount scheme to allow books to be cheaper so kids who don\u2019t have loads of money can afford them and so it\u2019s cheaper for schools to get new books and there should be student and NHS staff discounts in bookshops too.",
